-- MOVES-Trevor Manuel appointed senior adviser to Rothschild group
-- 
-- Tue Sep 30, 2014 01:40PM EDT
-- None



Sept 30 (Reuters) - Financial advisory services provider Rothschild [ROT.UL] said it appointed Trevor Manuel senior adviser to the group worldwide and deputy chairman of Rothschild in South Africa, effective Wednesday.

Manuel will be based in the company's Johannesburg office, Rothschild said in a statement. He was most recently minister in the presidency responsible for South Africa's National Planning Commission.